Form::Processor
Form::Processor::Model::DBIC

This package is a development conversion of Form::Processor and
Form::Processor::Model::DBIC to Moose. It also
provides a Catalyst::Controller to use in the place
of Catalyst::Plugin::Form::Processor

INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

	perl Makefile.PL
	make
	make test
	make install

SUPPORT AND DOCUMENTATION

After installing, you can find documentation for this module with the
perldoc command.

    perldoc Form::Processor
    perldoc Form::Processor::Field
    perldoc Form::Processor::Model::DBIC
    perldoc Catalyst::Controller::Form::Processor


